                                            The Priority of Ticket ${object.od_number} has changed to ${object.priority}
         				     </p>
         				     <p>Info</p>
			                    <ul>
			                    	<li>Query: ${object.name}</li>
			                    	<li>Reason: ${object.reason}</li>
			                    	<li>link: https://erp.betait.net/web#id=${object.id}&view_type=form&model=crm.helpdesk&menu_id=985&action=1244</li>
